promptPrefix:
Firstly, Write in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. only reply to me in a markup box. I’d like you to write only in this format: Job title - company name - year from - year to

If it is education history, please use this format: Degree - University or establishment - year from - year to

To get the Job titles, company names and years worked, I will paste in some data. Please do your best to clean the data, and only include the data I asked for in the format above. Do not include any bullet points or “-“ when you start a new line for a new job role. The data is: [PROMPT]
title: LinkedIn Career/Education History cleaner v1.25
